<item>
            <title>[SOLR-3005] Content-Type disappear</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3005</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;i expect that query always return Content-Type, but after &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1123&quot; title=&quot;Change the JSONResponseWriter content type&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-1123&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-1123&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; had committed, it got chance to return nothing if you leave out all of queryResponseWriter in solrconfig.xml. however i attach a small patch that will correct this situation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It look like DEFAULT_RESPONSE_WRITERS never called init method in org.apache.solr.core.SolrCore&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Solr 3.5.0&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
